                <li><strong>rc.24</strong>: same listener but with <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-foreground">!important</code> — cascade priority correct, but listener attaches after animation ends. Placebo.</li>
                <li><strong>rc.25</strong>: <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-foreground">getAnimations() + .finished promises + setProperty important</code> — race-free AND cascade-correct. Empirically verified.</li>
